channel.title: Looking thru the scripts
channel.description:
Looking thru all the scripts i notice most are for skilling up(which no point because u eventually get banned making that skilled up pointless) Or make very little money..like 30k a hour or do pointless things.
So im wondering.. what scripts could be made to actually make some good money? Ive only got minor script writing experience when i did scripts for macroqeust when i played everquest. I made my own script to play my char in a group setting and earn myself aa's in a few diffrent zones when i was with friends.. so i do know some about it but it would take me a while and ill prolly have questions . sooo anyhow =) post your ideas.
